### Imperatives
| Hebrew | English |
|--------|---------|
| סְגֹר | close! |
| פְּתַח | open! |
| רְאֵה | see! |
| זְכֹר | remember! |
| בֹּאוּ | come! (plural) |

## Grammar

- Paal infinitive forms (לִסְגֹר, לִפְתֹּחַ)
- Paal imperative forms (masculine singular and plural)
- Adjectives in predicative position (סְגוּרָה, פְתוּחָה)
- Feminine agreement with nouns and adjectives
- Past tense narrative sequence with ו consecutive
